CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 9 reads: "Homemakers See Latest in Foods, Appliances...2. The catchy Braun Baking Company tune "brown on the outside, good on the inside," was heard at frequent intervals as Miss Eunice Brown passes out slices of delicious Town Talk bread...-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Eunice Brown standing in Braun Baking Company booth in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
